24th Aug 2014 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 2 Highlights

Stage 2 sees the peloton travel the 174km between Algeciras and San Fernando. Mainly flat with only a third category climb early in the day, it is a stage for the sprinters, though as they near the sea in the final run, the wind may make things hard to control. Presented by Gary Imlach, commentary by Anthony Mccrossan and Graham Jones with Matt Rendell the reporter at the roadside.
